* Microsoft Defender for Cloud Apps
** Cloud Discovery policies
*** Detect new high-volume or wide app use
*** Detect new risky or non-compliant app use
*** Detect use of unsanctioned business apps
*** Detect unusual usage patterns on your network
*** Detect anomalous cloud discovery behavior in storage apps that aren't sanctioned
*** Detect risky OAuth apps
** Threat protection policies
*** Detect and control user activity from unfamiliar locations
*** Detect suspicious activity from an \"on-leave\" employee
*** Detect and notify when outdated browser OS is used
*** Detect and alert when Admin activity is detected on risky IP addresses
*** Detect activities by service account from external IP addresses
*** Detect mass download (data exfiltration)
*** Detect potential Ransomware activity
*** Detect malware in the cloud
*** Detect rogue admin takeover
*** Detect suspicious inbox manipulation rules
*** Detect leaked credentials
*** Detect anomalous file downloads
*** Detect anomalous file shares by a user
*** Detect anomalous activities from infrequent country/region
*** Detect activity performed by a terminated user
** Information protection policies
*** Detect and prevent external sharing of sensitive data
*** Detect externally shared confidential data
*** Detect and encrypt sensitive data at rest
*** Detect stale externally shared data
*** Detect data access from an unauthorized location
*** Detect and protect confidential data store in a non-compliant SP site
*** Detect externally shared source code
*** Detect unauthorized access to group data
*** Detect publicly accessible S3 buckets
*** Detect and protect GDPR related data across file storage apps
*** Block downloads for external users in real time
*** Enforce read-only mode for external users in real time
*** Block upload of unclassified documents in real time
